---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Terms of Use"
  description="Terms of use for PlainProcedure. Information about acceptable use, disclaimers, and limitations of liability."
  breadcrumbs={[{ name: 'Home', href: '/' }, { name: 'Terms of Use' }]}
>
  <section class="py-8 md:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Terms of Use</h1>
      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-[var(--color-muted)] [&_h2]:text-[var(--color-foreground)] [&_strong]:text-[var(--color-foreground)]">
        <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> March 15, 2026</p>

        <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing and using PlainProcedure (plainprocedure.com), you agree to these Terms of Use. If you do not agree, please do not use this site.</p>

        <h2>Information Purpose</h2>
        <p>PlainProcedure is an informational resource that presents publicly available CMS Medicare data in a more accessible format. <strong>This site does not provide medical advice.</strong> The information should not be used as a substitute for professional medical consultation or to make healthcare decisions.</p>

        <h2>Accuracy and Completeness</h2>
        <p>While we strive to present accurate information, we make no warranties about the completeness, reliability, or accuracy of the data. CMS data may contain errors, may be outdated, or may not reflect current pricing. Always verify important information with your healthcare provider and insurance company.</p>

        <h2>No Professional Advice</h2>
        <p>Nothing on this site constitutes professional advice of any kind — whether medical, legal, financial, or otherwise. Any decisions you make based on information found here are solely your responsibility.</p>

        <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>The underlying government data presented on this site is in the public domain. Our original design, code, text, and organization of the data are copyrighted by Kiznis.Studio.</p>

        <h2>Advertising</h2>
        <p>This site displays advertisements through Google AdSense to support its operation. Ads are served by third parties and are subject to their own terms and privacy policies.</p>

        <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, PlainProcedure and Kiznis.Studio shall not be liable for any damages arising from your use of or inability to use this site.</p>

        <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We may update these terms at any time. Continued use of the site constitutes acceptance of any changes.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about these terms? Email <a href="mailto:hello@plainprocedure.com">hello@plainprocedure.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
